@startuml
title 미핏 - 계획 vs 최종 아키텍처 비교

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<plan>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFCDD2
  BorderColor #C62828
}
skinparam component<<added>> {
  BackgroundColor #C8E6C9
  BorderColor #2E7D32
}

package "수행 계획 (초기) — 단순 모놀리식" <<plan>> {
  component "사용자" as U_P
  component "React (Vite)" as FE_P <<plan>>
  component "Django REST" as BE_P <<plan>>
  component "PostgreSQL" as DB_P <<plan>>
  component "Celery Worker\n(단일 큐)" as W_P <<plan>>
  component "OpenAI API" as OAI_P <<plan>>

  U_P --> FE_P
  FE_P --> BE_P
  BE_P --> DB_P
  BE_P --> W_P
  W_P --> OAI_P
}

package "최종 — 12 마이크로서비스" <<added>> {
  component "사용자" as U_F
  component "Frontend\nReact 19 + FSD" as FE_F
  component "Backend\nDjango 6 + Channels" as BE_F
  database "Redis" as R_F
  database "PostgreSQL" as DB_F

  package "도메인별 Worker" <<added>> {
    component "analysis-resume" as AR_F <<added>>
    component "interview-analysis-report" as IAR_F <<added>>
    component "scraping" as SCR_F <<added>>
    component "analysis-stt" as STT_F <<added>>
  }

  component "voice-api\n(FastAPI)" as VA_F <<added>>

  package "AWS Event Pipeline" <<added>> {
    component "S3 + SNS + SQS" as MQ_F <<added>>
    component "Lambda 4종\n+ face-analyzer" as L_F <<added>>
  }

  component "LiteLLM Gateway\n(To-Be Bedrock)" as LLM_F <<added>>

  U_F --> FE_F
  FE_F --> BE_F : REST + WS + SSE
  BE_F --> DB_F
  BE_F --> R_F
  R_F --> AR_F
  R_F --> IAR_F
  R_F --> SCR_F
  R_F --> STT_F
  BE_F --> VA_F
  BE_F ..> MQ_F : 이벤트
  MQ_F --> L_F
  L_F --> MQ_F : step-complete
  IAR_F ..> LLM_F
  AR_F ..> LLM_F
}

note bottom
  변경 7 가지:
  1. 단일 Worker → 도메인별 Worker
  2. 단일 백엔드 → backend + voice-api 분리
  3. voice-api STT → analysis-stt 분리
  4. 동기 영상 → 이벤트 기반 비동기
  5. 단일 Lambda → 4종 + face-analyzer
  6. 단일 EC2 → k3s 클러스터
  7. 직접 OpenAI → LiteLLM Gateway 사전 도입
end note

footer MeFit - 단순 모놀리식 → 12 마이크로서비스 진화
@enduml
